This repository provides standalone wrappers and generation scripts for
HST COSMOS-backed multi-survey strong-lensing simulations.

Credit and dependency notice
----------------------------
This code depends on SLSim, the LSST Strong Lensing Simulation pipeline, for
strong-lensing populations, HST COSMOS catalog-source morphology support, and
simulation interfaces used by the generator.

SLSim project: https://github.com/LSST-strong-lensing/slsim
SLSim documentation: https://slsim.readthedocs.io
SLSim license: MIT

If you use this repository for research, cite and acknowledge SLSim according
to the SLSim citation guidance, and cite the underlying survey/instrument data
products and catalogs used in your run.
